### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@accessToken = YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### List all users (admin only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Search users
GET {{baseUrl}}/users?search=john&page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get user by ID
# @name getUser
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/USER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get user by email
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/email/test@example.com
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Create new user (admin only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "newuser@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePass123",
  "fullName": "New User",
  "phone": "0987654321",
  "role": "CUSTOMER"
}

### Update user
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/USER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Updated Name",
  "phone": "0123456789"
}

### Deactivate user
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/USER_ID_HERE/deactivate
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}